ade|SWI]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/artist/Diodato#charts|title=Diodato|website=hitparade.ch|accessdate=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Amore che vieni amore che vai\"\n| 2013\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"5\"| ''E forse sono pazzo''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ubriaco\"\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2014\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Babilonia\"\n| 69 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Se solo avessi un altro\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I miei demoni\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Eternit\u00e0\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| ''A ritrovar bellezza''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Mi si scioglie la bocca\"\n| 2016\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Cosa siamo diventati''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Di questa felicit\u00e0\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Cretino che sei\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{n/a|Non-album singles}} \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Adesso\"<br/><small>(with [[Roy Paci]])</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| 28 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Essere semplice\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Il commerciante\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''Che vita meravigliosa''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Non ti amo pi\u00f9\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Che vita meravigliosa\"\n| 51<br/><ref name=\"Week 7\">{{cite web|url=https://www.fimi.it/top-of-the-music/classifiche.kl#/charts/3/2020/7|title=Top Singoli \u2013 Classifica settimanale WK 7|publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]]|language=Italian|accessdate=15 February 2020}}</ref> || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Fai rumore]]\"\n| 2020\n| 1 || 36\n|\n* [[FIMI]]: Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI\">{{cite certification|region=Italy|artist=Diodato|type=single|accessdate=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Recipient \n! Result\n|-\n|